{"type":null,"faqId":48180,"title":"荣耀小K手表的表带有多长？什么材质？多大的小孩可以戴？","answer":"\"手表采用经典扣式设计，可以随意调节长短，基本适合4-10岁的所有儿童手腕。<br>\n<br>\n手表表盘尺寸：43mm×41mm×13.8mm，表带长端大概98mm，短端62mm，手表总长约200mm。表带戴到最小的孔上，周长是128mm，最大的孔上是183mm。<br>\n<br>\n注：由于表带是一体式的，没有明确的起始点，公差比较大，数据仅供参考。<br>\n<br>\n表带材质：安全、环保的弹性体橡胶材质TPU\"<br>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3845","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1446428710000,"seriesProductName":"K1-G01","visitedTimes":30,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"K1-G01,荣耀小K,儿童手表,K1,表带,表带长度,适合人群,年龄,表带长短","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}